{"tid":1023113,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"宜家有咩產品可以遠距離監察人地嘅血糖?","createTime":"2019-02-15T13:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T07:02:36.000Z","uid":140309,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd4ccab6b110104511bee0877632d595aa27d7e","tid":1023113,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"講少少背景先﹐家母有糖尿病﹐血糖過低係會死得人﹐最近試過兩三次朝早瞓醒發現佢血糖過低要叫白車﹐話雖呢d意外唔常見﹐但只要有一次無人發現就肯定死得﹐而我地又唔會成日喺屋企始終都有d擔心<br />\n所要想問有無d產品可以長時間畀老母戴住﹐keep住自動無創check血糖、有上網功能就算唔喺老母身邊都可以用電話知道佢嘅血糖度數同收到緊急通知、同有GPS功能<br />\n我查過fitbit揾到間血糖公司合作整血糖手錶﹐不過好似未出﹐都唔知有無上網同GPS功能"},{"pid":"9d7b7741b64c209064499275e0c951a8944f17af","tid":1023113,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:46:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be11b41fccb79bd199db29ced8574013c923560a","tid":1023113,"uid":38621,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"用依個好似得<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sr9grSu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsr9grSu.png&h=c939db5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b77cec79fcccc94925ea60fdacc995c98e5baaf","tid":1023113,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be11b41fccb79bd199db29ced8574013c923560a","tid":1023113,"uid":38621,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"用依個好似得<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sr9grSu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsr9grSu.png&h=c939db5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T13:51:42.000Z","msg":"我嘅諗法都唔算天馬行空啦<br />\n呢d技術宜家係有,就係唔知mix埋一齊有無姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163a2d344233b7292b2e60554106cd6c4f936fb2","tid":1023113,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco